        "timestamp": "2021-09-03 11:54:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nFrom what I understand,if AsyncConfig and notificationExecutor bean are not laoded by Spring then processDataUpdatedEvent form NotificationService is simply execusted synchronously.\n\n    @Async(\"notificationExecutor\")\n    public Future<Void> processDataUpdatedEvent(...)\n\nAm I correct ?",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
